---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import BargainingUnit from "../../images/2025_contract/we-won.png";
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Heading from "../../ui/typography/Heading.astro";
import Text from "../../ui/typography/Text.astro";
import Mark from "../../ui/Mark/Mark.astro";
import Surface from "../../ui/Surface/Surface.astro";
import Button from "../../ui/Button/Button.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<BaseLayout title="2025 Contract">
  <section class="contract-hero">
    <Heading as="h1" size="xl" maxLineLength={false}>Our New Contract</Heading>
    <Text as="p" size="lg" class="contract-hero__subtitle">
      Ratified December 5, 2025 - after a <Mark variant="amber">historic 42-day strike</Mark>.
    </Text>
  </section>

  <div class="contract-photo col-[wide]">
    <Image
      alt="A screenshot of a Zoom meeting where our Bargaining Unit members were celebrating their new contract and the conclusion of their strike"
      src={BargainingUnit}
    />
  </div>

  <section class="contract-body">
    <Text as="p">
      On December 5, 2025, 98% of our union voted YES to ratify
      a new collective bargaining agreement. Kickstarter United bargained
      for over 7 months and undertook a historic 42-day-long strike in order to
      secure vital new protections and benefits that we hope will not only
      improve the lives of our members, but will also serve as an inspiration to
      working people everywhere. All of these wins also come in addition to
      the benefits from our first contract, with no major concessions from the union.

      Some of the improvements we won in this new contract include:
    </Text>
  </section>

  <Surface elevation={1} class="contract-wins">
    <Heading as="h2" size="md">What We Won</Heading>
    <ul class="contract-wins__list">
      <li><Icon name="tabler:calendar-check" size={20} class="contract-wins__icon" /> Strong protections for the 4-day work week that Kickstarter and our workers have thrived under</li>
      <li><Icon name="tabler:coin" size={20} class="contract-wins__icon" /> A minimum salary based on an Annual Living Wage Review</li>
      <li><Icon name="tabler:chart-bar" size={20} class="contract-wins__icon" /> Salary benchmarking annually to ensure pay is keeping up with the market</li>
      <li><Icon name="tabler:robot" size={20} class="contract-wins__icon" /> New protections against uses of AI which would replace workers</li>
      <li><Icon name="tabler:trending-up" size={20} class="contract-wins__icon" /> Even better terms for our profit-sharing bonus pool</li>
      <li><Icon name="tabler:heart-rate-monitor" size={20} class="contract-wins__icon" /> Up to a week of paid leave in case of a miscarriage</li>
      <li><Icon name="tabler:beach" size={20} class="contract-wins__icon" /> The ability to roll over a week's worth of PTO into the new year</li>
      <li><Icon name="tabler:shield-check" size={20} class="contract-wins__icon" /> Strengthened protections against the use of subcontractors to replace union workers</li>
      <li><Icon name="tabler:plus" size={20} class="contract-wins__icon" /> Plus plenty of other small but meaningful improvements</li>
    </ul>
  </Surface>

  <section class="contract-cta">
    <Text as="p">
      You can read a full copy of our contract (with the signatures omitted) here.
      We're happy to share it for others to help build their contracts in the
      tech industry. If you have any questions about our contract, please feel free to use our contact
      form. We'll try to answer at our earliest convenience.
    </Text>
    <div class="contract-cta__actions">
      <Button as="a" href="/Ratified_2025_CBA_KSRU.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" variant="primary">
        Read the Full Contract
      </Button>
      <Button as="a" href="/contracts/2022" variant="ghost">
        2022 Contract
      </Button>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .contract-hero {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: var(--ksru-space-sm);
    margin-block: var(--ksru-space-2xl) var(--ksru-space-xl);
  }

  .contract-hero__subtitle {
    color: color-mix(in oklch, currentColor, transparent 30%);
    text-wrap: balance;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .contract-photo {
    margin-bottom: var(--ksru-space-2xl);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;

    @supports (corner-shape: squircle) {
      corner-shape: squircle;
      border-radius: 32px;
    }
  }

  .contract-photo :global(img) {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .contract-body {
    margin-bottom: var(--ksru-space-xl);
  }

  .contract-wins {
    padding: var(--ksru-space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--ksru-space-2xl);
  }

  .contract-wins__list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--ksru-space-sm);
    margin: var(--ksru-space-md) 0 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .contract-wins__list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--ksru-space-sm);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .contract-wins__icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--ksru-emerald-500);
    translate: 0 3px;
  }

  .contract-cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--ksru-space-2xl);
  }

  .contract-cta__actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--ksru-space-sm);
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: var(--ksru-space-lg);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
